## Debug in production.

<PageDescription>

Diagnostic reports provide a view into running Node.js processes—_without_ attaching a debugger.

**<Metadata prop="packageName"/>** builds upon these capabilities by providing _safe_ analysis and transformation of diagnostic reports.

</PageDescription>
